own what do you want to tell Chairman Xi<br />\n3. Post your work on instagram, facebook and twitter with tag #Xinnie the Pooh<br />\n4. Tag up to 3 more friends to ask them draw together!<br />\n5. Those who are tagged also join to draw Xinnie the Pooh, keep drawing until Chairman Xi can see our works!!"},{"pid":"38df4d435d4f3f28f511ae27b940a993858af7da","tid":1640622,"uid":14845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T06:12:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/senrubiopress/status/1181662591871000576?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsenrubiopress%2Fstatus%2F1181662591871000576%3Fs%3D21&d=h%2FIbyvsQTNyUi2WbZ%2BJFJ7ccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=537e71f9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsenrubiopress%2Fstatus%2F1181662591871000576%3Fs%3D21&h=9102c2e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/senrubiopress/status/1181662591871000576?s=21</a>"}]}